== English ==
=== Etymology ===
*The term was coined as an [[insidious]] extension of the [[Black Legend]]. 
=== Noun ===
'''White Legend'''
*The term [[purport]]s to present the "other" side of the defamatory anti-Hispanic [[Black Legend]] (in Spanish [[Leyenda Negra]]) by claiming that all well documented and academically accepted historical facts favorable to the [[Spanish]] or to [[Hispanic]]s generally are, in reality, exaggerated praise of the Spanish or of Hispanics, and are therefore suspect. 
